tool_description: This API provides various endpoints to collect data from youtube such as video complete information, downloading videos, streams, playlist information, channel information, and downloading videos in one go from a channel or a target playlist.
name: YouTube Powerfull API
title: YouTube Powerfull API

api_list.name: GET Video Keywords
api_list.description: By Providing The Video Link You can GET the Video Keywords
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://youtube-powerfull-api.p.rapidapi.com/api/get_video_kewords/9t_ufVYBcds/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "youtube-powerfull-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
api_list.convert_code:
import requests

url = "https://youtube-powerfull-api.p.rapidapi.com/api/get_video_kewords/{video_id}/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "youtube-powerfull-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: GET Video's Full Details || Provide the Video ID
api_list.description:
Retrieve full information about a video by simply providing the video ID.  
If you don't know where to find the video ID ? kindly check the bellow example.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=**nu_pCVPKzTk**
As you see in the above link a string inside the double stars is the video ID.

            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "youtube-powerfull-api.p.rapidapi.com"
